## Chapter 11 The Product Designer

* "Modern product designers continuously collaborate with product managers and engineers from discovery and delivery."
* "Rather than being measured on the output of their design work, the product designer is measured on the success of the product."
* UX is critical importance to the success of the product. UX includes all touch points with the product (offline and online).
* "Good product designers think about the customer's journey over time as they interact with the product and with the company as a whole."
* "Good product designers use prototypes as their primary canvas for communicating ideas, both internally and externally."
* "Good product designers are constantly testing their ideas with real users and customers."

